        <updateDate>2024-01-12T14:07:21Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;National Weather Service Communications Improvement Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the National Weather Service (NWS) to replace NWSChat with a commercial, off-the-shelf communications solution that is hosted on the public cloud. (NWSChat is an instant messaging program used by NWS personnel to share, in real-time, critical warnings and other types of weather information.)&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
